article.description: — Shaquan Jules scored 11 points and grabbed 14 rebounds and made 1 of 2 foul shots to help send Radford to a 54-51 win over Hampton on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Jules lifts Radford over Hampton 54-51
article.story: RADFORD, Va. -- — Shaquan Jules scored 11 points and grabbed 14 rebounds and made 1 of 2 foul shots to help send Radford to a 54-51 win over Hampton on Wednesday night. Najee Garvin missed a 3-pointer for the Pirates to end it. Hampton put up a season-low 23 points after halftime. Dravon Mangum scored 13 points and had eight rebounds for Radford (6-11, 2/3 Big South Conference). Russell Dean scored 14 points for the Pirates (4-10, 0-3), whose losing streak stretched to four games. Garvin scored 11, Dajour Dickens had 10 points, 10 rebounds and blocked four shots and DeAngelo Epps grabbed 10 rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
